     * @param {string} tableFieldName - name of field ( given in property card in designer)
     * @param {tableInit|editorClick|editorValueChange|editorFocus|editorBlur|sortChange|pageChange|itemsPerPageChange} type - name of the event
     * @param {object} args - specific to event type arguments.
     * @param {string} [args.columnName] - name of a column where event is happening
     * @param {number} [args.rowId] - index of a row where event is happening
     * @param {string|number|boolean} [args.value] - value of an editor passed in `editorValueChange` event
     * @param {asc|desc} [args.direction] - sorting direction for a column
     * @param {number} [args.page] - page number for changing page event
