     *    - editorValueChange
     *        - columnName
     *        - rowId
     *        - value
     *
     *    - editorFocus
     *        - columnName
     *        - rowId
     *
     *    - editorBlur
     *        - columnName
     *        - rowId
     *
     *    - sortChange
     *        - columnName
     *        - direction
     *
     *    - pageChange
     *       - page
     *
     *    - itemsPerPageChange
     *       - itemsPerPageChange
     * @example
     * Example of implementation:
     *
     * ExtensionClass.prototype.onDynamicTableEvent = function(tableFieldName, type, args) {
